Research Article
Comprehensive Mutation Analysis for Congenital Muscular Dystrophy: A Clinical PCR-Based Enrichment and Next-Generation Sequencing Panel

    C. Alexander Valencia equal contributor ,

    equal contributor Contributed equally to this work with: C. Alexander Valencia, Arunkanth Ankala

